---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Editorial Policy"
  description="Read the editorial standards Simple Calculators uses for calculator content, assumptions, updates, and corrections."
>
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Editorial Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-600">
        This page explains how calculator content is prepared, reviewed, and updated on Simple Calculators.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Content standards</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
        <li>We prioritize clarity, practical usefulness, and transparent assumptions.</li>
        <li>Each major calculator page should explain method, limits, and suitable use cases.</li>
        <li>We avoid publishing pages that are only minor wording variations of existing tools.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">How updates happen</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
        <li>We review formulas and assumptions when calculators are revised.</li>
        <li>We update copy when guidance becomes unclear or potentially misleading.</li>
        <li>We periodically add worked examples and edge-case notes based on user feedback.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Corrections policy</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
        If you notice an issue, email us at
        <a href="mailto:hello@simplecalculators.io" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 underline ml-1">hello@simplecalculators.io</a>.
        We review reported errors and publish corrections as quickly as practical.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Independence and monetization</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
        We may use advertising and affiliate links to support operations. Monetization does not change calculation formulas,
        recommendations, or disclosure of assumptions.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
